It was born from my love of the skin textures and photorealistic look in Dreamlike Photoreal and my hate of how difficult it was to pose people in unorthodox ways. It's capable of some hardcore, but not the focus of the model at all, and therefore it's very hard to prompt.

The blend includes Dreamlike Photoreal, so here's the license. You have to follow it.
